data.description: Check out this 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom haven nestled in the heart of Ozark, MO. This nicely updated home offers the perfect blend of seclusion and convenience, making it a great option for any buyer. Step inside and be captivated by the updates and amenities this home offers! With its spacious layout and thoughtfully designed floor plan, this sanctuary is ideal for both entertaining and unwinding. Multiple living areas provide ample space for hosting memorable gatherings with loved ones, while a serene flat yard with a deck and patio offers the perfect backdrop for outdoor enjoyment. The kitchen is beautifully updated and spacious! That's not all, the water heater is less than 1 year old, the hvac system is less than 2 years old AND the seller will include a brand new roof to help ensure many years of worry-free living for you!
